    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏背景</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >艾德鲁大陆一直维持着和平与宁静，邪恶的力量已被封印许久。然而随着邪恶力量的再次苏醒，作为勇者的你被再次召唤，与黑暗的力量进行殊死搏斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏为国产第三人称RPG卡通风格类游戏，女性主角。有着多种多样的技能设计：背刺，弹反，反击，追击，连击，以及主动技能等。通过解锁新的技能，活用各种主动技能和被动技能，你将变得更加强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099680/extras/5ef607e1af7c8e3c98e8fa7073e7f57c.poster.avif?t=1752211169\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099680/extras/5ef607e1af7c8e3c98e8fa7073e7f57c.webm?t=1752211169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099680/extras/5ef607e1af7c8e3c98e8fa7073e7f57c.mp4?t=1752211169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br>随着剧情的深入，会有不同的角色加入队伍。玩家可以控制新加入的角色，并且每一个角色有自己独特的天赋技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099680/extras/0872c7883940670ea648b27d2ad90ea0.poster.avif?t=1752211169\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099680/extras/0872c7883940670ea648b27d2ad90ea0.webm?t=1752211169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099680/extras/0872c7883940670ea648b27d2ad90ea0.mp4?t=1752211169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的敌人种类繁多：有近战类型，远攻类型，魔法类型以及巨型生物，不同的怪物有不同的攻击特点，掌握敌人的攻击特点是你成功打败敌人的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏拥有丰富的场景：山间，树林，城堡，地牢，洞穴，雪地等。游戏属于卡通类型，选用虚幻引擎5制作，塞尔达风格类场景！</p>",
